/* ==========================================
   JAMES TALK TOPICS — COMMON PHASE, LEVEL 1
   phase === "common" && friendshipLevel === 1

   CHARACTER: James Holt, Chef at Ruby's Diner
   → Late 30s, married with kids. Runs the kitchen.
   → Tired, sometimes grumpy during a rush, but fair.
   → Treats player like a regular kid stopping by.

   COMMON L1 TONE:
   → Player has no job, just dropped by.
   → James chats from the kitchen pass or while prepping.

   CONTEXTS:
   dinerRubys_common_morning
   dinerRubys_common_afternoon
   dinerRubys_common_evening
========================================== */

