<<narrative>>James aggressively chops an onion, looking annoyed.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "dinerChef">>Supplier brought the wrong onions again. I asked for yellow, I get white.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Is there a difference?<</dialog>>
