            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/james/level1/jamesCommonMorning-2.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>James eyes a clipboard hanging over the grill.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "dinerChef">>Morning. Don't mind me, just counting how many eggs we have left.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Not enough?<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerChef">>Never enough. Saturday mornings wipe us out completely. It's a logistical nightmare.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>You'll figure it out.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerChef">>I always do. Have a good one.<</dialog>`,
                friendship: 1, trust: 0
            },
            {
text: `<<set _img = "assets/content/scenes/interactions/james/level1/jamesCommonMorning-3.webp">>
<<image _img "100%">>
<<narrative>>James scrubs a clean-looking spot on his apron with his thumb.<</narrative>>
<<dialog "dinerChef">>My kid got jam on my work clothes this morning. I've washed it three times.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>It barely shows.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerChef">>I know it's there. Sticky. You don't have kids, you wouldn't get it.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>I guess not.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerChef">>Count your blessings.<</dialog>`,
                friendship: 2, trust: 1
