<<dialog "dinerChef">>This is my fourth cup today. The baby kept me up all night.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>You should get some sleep.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "dinerChef">>Sleep is a luxury. I run a kitchen. Go enjoy your morning, kid.<</dialog>>
<<dialog "player">>Will do, James.<</dialog>`,
                friendship: 2, trust: 0
